WEBVTT

1
00:07:07.710 --> 00:07:09.300 
我小的时候
When I was a boy,

2
00:07:09.380 --> 00:07:11.300 
只要一有空
I spent all my spare time

3
00:07:11.380 --> 00:07:17.010 
就会跑来这个地方 在石壁上寻找被埋葬的宝物
searching through rocks in places like this... for buried treasure.

4
00:07:20.270 --> 00:07:21.100 
化石
Fossils.

5
00:07:22.810 --> 00:07:25.110 
这种生物叫斑彩螺
It's a creature called an aonite.

6
00:07:25.190 --> 00:07:28.570 
这种动物活着时 住在这边的壳房里
And in life the animal itself lived in the chamber here

7
00:07:28.650 --> 00:07:31.650 
它会伸出触须抓住猎物
and spread out its tentacles to catch its prey.

8
00:07:32.780 --> 00:07:36.910 
它活在一亿八千万年前的地球上
And it lived about 180 million years ago.

